Fresh Seafood with prices you can't beat.  This is pretty much a seafood market that cooks for you and is self service, even busing your own table....BUT...considering that we had 750g of sushi grade Tuna for only $16 (which was grilled perfectly) ....I would have swept the floors (and had my wife clean the toilets) for them !!  Also had 1kg of steamed shrimp and Chicharrones.  Add bread,  salad, beer and a glass of wine and we were a family of four  stuffed for $60 !!
